# upload_irida_fast5
# upload a fast5 file to a sample in IRIDA
#
# usage: upload_irida_fast5 PROJECT_ID SAMPLE_ID FILE_PATH
#
# NOTE: endpoint is /api/samples/{id}/fast5, not /api/samples/{id}/sequenceFiles/fast5.
# Confirmed working as non-admin on VIGASP 23.01.3. RBAC gap - see GitHub issue #12.
#
# example: upload_irida_fast5 150:test_gmarselis 11745:ZZTEST_SAMPLE_DO_NOT_USE /path/to/file.fast5
